The paper proposes a new method for simultaneous clustering and optimization in graph datasets. This falls under the broad category of machine learning and data analysis, which is covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a new method for clustering and optimization. "cs.DS" (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses an efficient algorithm based on ADMM. "cs.SI" (Social and Information Networks) is another possible category as the paper deals with graph datasets. "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) and "cs.CV" (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are less likely but still possible as the paper deals with machine learning and data analysis.
